{"tid":2112062,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"北京安撫東盟 否認南海建「帝國」","createTime":"2020-07-17T04:40:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-17T08:15:45.000Z","uid":25558,"like":9,"dislike":77,"uniUserReply":78,"replies":[{"pid":"30a683e9962657b593a32b0f5d8aec6641c0c138","tid":2112062,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T04:40:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200717/R4XUGH23ATNTJC23U5FAVT344M/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200717%2FR4XUGH23ATNTJC23U5FAVT344M%2F&d=6SBmejzB2pOSQzgprEhHpYWZOtE43EI%2FqUWggxD1P9E%3D&h=6d45a0fd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200717%2FR4XUGH23ATNTJC23U5FAVT344M%2F&h=8569b832\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200717/R4XUGH23ATNTJC23U5FAVT344M/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n北京安撫東盟 否認南海建「帝國」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/pvd6_94zPtzYPKs_KdD01fy1M4Q=/481x361/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/XRMP5YCA5XZRQTEAD3LQVMR3EY.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fpvd6_94zPtzYPKs_KdD01fy1M4Q%3D%2F481x361%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FXRMP5YCA5XZRQTEAD3LQVMR3EY.gif&h=9a63152b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鄧錫軍<br />\n<br />\n美國批評中國在南海作為儼如流氓，和東盟討論「南海行為準則」時欺負東盟後，中國駐東盟大使鄧錫軍立即撲火，公開安撫東盟，否認中國謀求在南海建立「海洋帝國」，強調將盡早重啟磋商「南海行為準則」，探討新的海上合作方式。中國專家警告，中方要做好南海形勢變壞的準備，致力於透過能力建設形成威懾力，以達到不戰而屈人之兵的目的。<br />\n<br />\n鄧錫軍接受印尼《雅加達郵報》。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n駐東盟大使稱重啟磋商<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：華府狙擊中國科企 研禁抖音微信<br />\n<br />\n中國南海研究院院長吳士存表示，中國宣佈設立「南海防空識別區」未必能打痛美國，反而或。。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n中新網/《環球時報》"},{"pid":"a68b745e14f3ef57716df55a6385e198afe65c0a","tid":2112062,"uid":38904,"like":68,"dislike":3,"score":65,"citedBy":9,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T04:43: